        <p>Around Porto you'll find several similar tiled churches, including the <strong>Church of Saint Ildefonso</strong> with its tiled facade, and the <strong>Chapel of Souls</strong> with its exterior completely covered in blue and white azulejo tiles that make up elaborate designs.</p>
        <!-- Read More Read Less Tab -->
