        <h3>Bolsa Palace</h3>
        <p>The city's most famous palace is the 19th century <strong>Bolsa Palace</strong>, which showcases incredibly lavish ornate interiors that you can tour. The Bolsa Palace is definitely a must-see attraction.</p>
        <h3>Monument Church os St.&nbsp;Francis</h3>
        <p>Next door to the palace is the impressive baroque 14th century <strong>Monument Church of St. Francis</strong>, which features extravagant interiors covered in gold and underground catacombs.</p>
