            <p>One more attraction to consider is the 19th century <strong>Gardens of the Crystal Palace</strong>, which feature beautiful manicured gardens overlooking the river from high above, located to the west of Porto's historic centre. Another great place to take in views over the river is from the Parque das Virtudes park.</p>
